---
title: Uruguayan-Style Churrasco Steaks with Chimichurri, Roasted Potatoes & Corn Salad
description: Get to know Latin American cuisine this Hispanic Heritage Month, and unite your familia around this vibrant Uruguayan-style dish! Juicy slices of bavette steak are drizzled with bright, herbaceous chimichurri sauce. On the side, you’ll savor the sabor of golden brown roasted potato wedges and a creamy chili-lime charred corn salad!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ba30b0fb4859096c8b6191-bcb5df9d.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66ba30b0fb4859096c8b6191-en-US.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/uruguayan-style-churrasco-steaks-66ba30b0fb4859096c8b6191
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 830 kcal
  fat: 50 g
